##Mauritius - Postal History
##Literature and Links

### Philatelic Publications

{{em: The Postal History of Mauritius}} by Edward B. Proud. Although published in 2001 limits itself to pre-independence 1968. Unless otherwise indicated all the post office opening and closing dates have been taken from this book. Other references are indicated by a (E.B.Proud) following.

Mauritius Postal History and Stamps by Peter Ibbotson, Published in 1991, together with Revisions and Additions published in 1995. References from this have a (Ibbotson) following.

